This repository contains build tooling only (Dockerfile, shell scripts, CI
configuration and documentation) for producing a native arm64 container image
of code_aster. These build files are released under the MIT License (below).

code_aster itself, and its prerequisites, are downloaded from the official EDF
GitLab during the image build and are governed by their own licenses —
principally the GNU General Public License v3 (GPLv3) for code_aster. The
produced container image therefore contains GPLv3 software. See
https://www.code-aster.org/ and https://gitlab.com/codeaster/src.

